original: Carlberg, Ernst, kyrkoherde, Unde-näs, f. 28/2/08 i Sthlm. G. m. Anna Stina Prytz. Barn: Gunnar f. 37, Birgitta 40. — Stud:ex. i Vänersb. 27, teol. fil. ex. 29, teol. kand. samt prakt, teol. prov 34, prästv. f. Skara stift 35. Tjg. s. v. pastor i Synnerby, Undenäs O’. Skölvene, assist, v. sv. sjömanskyrkan i Hull, kontr :adj. i Norrbottens norra kontr., past:adj. i Lidköp. samt v. kommin. i Götene, kommin. i Nykyrka 39, kyrkoh. i Undenäs sed. 47.
translated: Carlberg, Ernst, parish priest, Unde-näs, born on February 28, 1908 in Stockholm. Married to Anna Stina Prytz. Children: Gunnar, born in 1937, Birgitta, born in 1940. He graduated from Vänersborg High School in 1927, obtained a degree in theology in 1929, a degree in practical theology and passed the theological examination in 1934. He was ordained as a priest in the Skara diocese in 1935. He served as assistant pastor in Synnerby, Undenäs and Skölvene, assistant at the Swedish Seamen's Church in Hull, district curate in the northern district of Norrbotten, parish curate in Lidköping, assistant curate in Götene, curate in Nykyrka in 1939, and parish priest in Undenäs since 1947.
